&lt;p&gt;Theranos shocked me. Before joining uni, Holmes was a role model to me - she was
going to make it big despite being so young. Part of me wants to understand that
she wasn&amp;rsquo;t a villain through and through. Maybe she was an inventor who built
magnificent castles on a foundation of sand.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>U.S. Files Criminal Charges Against Elizabeth Holmes and Ramesh Balwani [WSJ]</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/health-and-medicine/2018-06-15-theranos-disaster/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Jun 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/health-and-medicine/2018-06-15-theranos-disaster/</guid><description>&lt;div class="citation" citation-icon-class='fas fa-fw fa-globe' cited-by-count='' is-main=''&gt;
